ooth sailing.  New New tweaks and enhancements in this release:  Fixed Bugs that were squashed in&#8230;</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/event-tickets/event-tickets-5-7-1/\">Event Tickets 5.7.1</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Leopoldo Scanavino\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4310:\"\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-45 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.3%\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-summary\">Summary</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"release-label has-normal-font-size\">Maintenance Release</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"release-summary__overview has-medium-font-size\">The latest version of Event Tickets includes PHP 8+ compatibility work as well as additional fixes and tweaks. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>As always, we recommend <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/creating-and-using-a-wordpress-staging-site/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">testing updates</a> on a staging site first, but it should all be smooth sailing.<br></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-48 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-new\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2728.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> New</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">New tweaks and enhancements in this release:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Prevented Single Attendee endpoint from throwing a notice on PHP 8+.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Attendees listed on the <code>Your Tickets</code> section will now match the order they were entered in.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>New notice to communicate to users, of Wallet Plus availability on the Attendees page.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>New notice to communicate to users, of Wallet Plus availability on Tickets Emails settings page.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Added attendee name to attendees list after purchase or registration.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Added filter <code>tec_tickets_commerce_gateway_stripe_webhook_valid_key_polling_attempts</code> to allow the modification of how many attempts Tickets Commerce will poll for Stripe webhooks for validation.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Included Wallet Plus info notice on Add-Ons Page. </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Included Wallet Plus info notice on Help Page. </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-51 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-fixed\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2705.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Fixed</h4>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Bugs that were squashed in this release:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Tickets Commerce Stripe webhooks correctly handles internally validating the Secret Signing key.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tickets Commerce Stripe Charge and Payment Intent webhooks no longer create duplicated success emails for a single ticket purchase.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-54 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.3%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-translations\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5e3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Translations</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Updated language files and strings:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>10 new strings added</li>\n\n\n\n<li>96 updated</li>\n\n\n\n<li>1 fuzzied</li>\n\n\n\n<li>0 obsoleted</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/event-tickets/event-tickets-5-7-1/\">Event Tickets 5.7.1</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"The Events Calendar 6.2.8.2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:163:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/the-events-calendar/the-events-calendar-6-2